---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
  <strong class="statement site">
    <img class="logo" src="/logo/monochrome.svg" alt="Moment Logo" />
    <span>Moment 是練習作品</span><span class="divideDot">・</span><span class="sponsor"><a class="authorLink"
        href="https://read.cv/ymcheung" target="_blank" rel="noopener">We</a>
      Built this Project on Rock &lsquo;n Roll and Your Support.</span>
  </strong>
  <p class="statement normal">此網站上收錄的歌詞、電影與影劇的智慧財產權皆屬於原作者。</p>
  <figure class="statement fromTw">
    <img class="mapTaiwan" src="/taiwan.png" alt="台灣圖示" loading="lazy">
    <figcaption class="mit">
      台灣製造 {year}
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</footer>

<style lang="scss">
  footer {
    grid-area: footer;
    padding: 0 16px calc(3rem + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
    font-family: var(--font-body);

    @media screen and (min-width: 1200px) {
      padding: 0 0 calc(3rem + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
    }
  }

  .logo {
    vertical-align: text-bottom;
  }

  .statement {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 20px;
  }

  .site {
    color: hsl(var(--color-shade1000));
  }

  .divideDot {
    display: none;

    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
      display: inline;
    }
  }

  .sponsor {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;

    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
      display: inline;
      margin-top: initial;
    }
  }

  .authorLink {
    color: inherit;
  }

  .normal {
    color: hsl(var(--color-shade1000));
  }

  .fromTw {
    display: grid;
    grid: auto / 15px 1fr;
    column-gap: 6px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mapTaiwan {
    width: 15px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .mit {
    color: hsl(var(--color-shade1000));
  }
</style>
